      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5a3963a8-cf1f-11e3-84da-52540035b04c).  Ran 21 tests.  4 tests failed: lnet-selftest, sanity-quota, replay-single, sanity.",
